Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:08.32,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:12.93,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.63,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.26,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:17.43,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:19.80,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:22.77,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:25.40,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:39.87,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:42.51,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:51.23,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean\Nwas the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:57.53,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has killed\Nthe dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:03.41,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:07.16,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:11.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:20.17,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,After a fierce battle, the Straw Hat Pirates\Nhave finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:23.13,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,the strongest sea, ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:26.97,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The crew received a distress call and landed on Punk Hazard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:31.86,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,a bizarre island that is split\Nbetween a burning side and a frozen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:35.25,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Both the Straw Hats and Smoker...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:40.75,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,are nuisances who\Ncould reveal this island to the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.01,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,We'll take both of them out in one stroke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.62,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Send word to Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.20,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:51.57,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,I could never even figure out\Nwhy you joined the Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.04,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,What is your goal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.68,Main,Law,0,0,0,,There are things you can't see unless you move...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.86,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.54,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,My heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:35.02,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I don't have to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.45,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:25.97,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Tashigi-chan, he's way too strong for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.16,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Please let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:31.47,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,I didn't become a marine just to\Nlet someone else protect me at times like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:34.60,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,If you go back under that curtain,\Nyou'll just get cut to pieces again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.52,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Just leave this to Smokey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.28,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,The curtain's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.99,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Alright, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.46,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Go, Crocotaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.47,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.20,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.69,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Isn't that a warship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:03.01,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Does that mean the Navy's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:06.01,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,What?!  There wasn't anything here earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:09.92,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,What's going on?!  Did something happen to Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.37,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,There's somebody over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.71,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh?  Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:18.37,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey!  Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:21.56,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Imagine meeting you!  It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.93,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything you've done for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.27,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Straw-Hatter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.10,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.45,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,the guy we met in the Human Shop on Sabaody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.51,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Trafalgar Law.  But now, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.74,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Right, Trafal... Traf!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:43.67,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That guy helped me escape\Nduring the Whitebeard war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.57,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,And he even treated my injuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.45,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:51.56,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He saved my life, just like Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.23,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:59.33,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd meet you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:02.81,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Really, thanks a lot for before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.67,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.64,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Where's the talking bear and those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:11.36,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Bring Straw-Hatter over here! {Copy-paste from 487}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.95,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take him away from this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.66,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Let me take care of him for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.08,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor! {End copy-paste from 487}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:23.03,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,Where is Ace?! {Copy-paste from 491}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.21,Flashbacks,Jinbe,0,0,0,,What'll happen if we just let him be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.95,Flashbacks,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Well, to put it bluntly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.10,Flashbacks,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Like I said when we came to this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.72,Flashbacks,Jinbe,0,0,0,,if his wounds reopen, he'll probably die.{End copy-paste from 491}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:39.21,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Straw-Hatter will need complete rest\Nfor another two weeks. {The script-search indicates that this scene is not from a previous episode.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:42.27,Flashbacks,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,Understood.  Thanks for all you've done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.82,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I'm impressed that you survived, Straw-Hatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:52.22,Main,Law,0,0,0,,But there is no need to feel indebted to me\Nfor saving you back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:56.12,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I was just acting on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:08:00.45,Main,Law,0,0,0,,We are both pirates.  Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:02.69,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:05.24,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If we're both going for One Piece then that makes us enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:08.77,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,but I still owe a debt to a lot of people after what happened two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:12.57,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,How lucky that I got to meet you\Nright after meeting Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.63,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Really, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:19.14,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey!  There's a collapsed marine over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:26.25,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Isn't... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:29.29,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Hey... Please save me, Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.82,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:38.80,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.43,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Smoker-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.27,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,{\i1}Smokey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.21,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.54,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,W-What?  Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.87,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey, this isn't good, Luffy!  The Navy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:54.51,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.08,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Captain-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.24,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Smokey, are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.12,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:12.40,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I knew it, it's Old Smokey and his group!\NThat sure takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.16,Thoughts,Tashigi,0,0,0,,There's a hole... in his...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.92,Thoughts,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:26.25,Flashbacks,Marine,0,0,0,,In order to become a Warlord...{Copy-paste from 584}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:30.45,Flashbacks,Marine,0,0,0,,he delivered the hearts\Nof one hundred pirates to Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.13,Flashbacks,Marine,0,0,0,,He's completely deranged!{End copy-paste from 584}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.81,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.27,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,How could you?!  How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:52.27,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.47,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Hey now, stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.48,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I can't stand... such crudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:14.03,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.44,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Dammit!  He got her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.54,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Even Smo-san is down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.60,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What did he just do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.78,Main,Law,0,0,0,,You never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.24,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Don't get so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.22,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.78,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Luffy, hurry up!  We're in danger here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:45.29,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.96,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, Traf!  I wanted to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.59,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Go behind the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:56.06,Main,Law,0,0,0,,You'll find what you're looking for there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:11:00.13,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll meet again.\NWe both have something we want back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.78,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,He must mean me, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.75,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,This is dangerous!  I'm a former pirate as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:14.62,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Alright, Luffy!  We've gotta get away from the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.26,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I wonder if Smokie's group will be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.76,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Were they defeated by Traf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.04,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,That's Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.11,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.64,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Stop it, this isn't the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:39.30,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Smo-san and Captain-chan are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.93,Main,Child,0,0,0,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.96,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What can we do?  The children won't last much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.44,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll cut off my fur and give it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Stop it!  That's my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:07.07,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You say that, but there aren't\Nany other warm coats around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.91,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's a mountain hut nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:13.53,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Oh, a camera, a mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.63,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,and a s-shower!  A mountain hut would have those!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.84,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tie you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.55,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Who's who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.88,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Law is so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:24.43,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I see that I have no other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.83,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Put a leaf on each of your heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.44,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Huh?!  This isn't the time for nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.94,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The kids are about to collapse from the cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:36.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Besides, there isn't a single plant on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:37.44,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,So there aren't any leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:41.41,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Then use rocks or something else, it matters not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.11,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Make haste!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:47.58,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Fine... It seems like you got some sort of plan here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:49.27,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I'll find rocks for the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.42,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,We've done it.  So, what's up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:02.75,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,If this is just some silly superstition to make the cold go away,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:03.80,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I'm gonna flatten you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:04.72,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:14.81,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Doron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:18.34,Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:20.61,Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.19,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,We've got coats!  And shoes too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.04,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,How?!  What did he do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.47,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:37.98,Main,Child,0,0,0,,It's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.20,Main,Child,0,0,0,,It's so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:43.54,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,The truth is, I consumed a rare kind of fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:48.18,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,and ever since, I have been able to use magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:51.68,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,to change any object into a disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:55.05,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I am not familiar with clothing from foreign lands, but will these do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:59.77,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Though I must warn you that it's magic,\Nso the clothes will vanish if you remove them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.95,Main,Child,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yay, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:06.20,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hmph, don't go overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.56,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You've got Devil Fruit powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.95,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Pardon me?  Devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.12,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:16.83,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,If you could do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.40,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,{\i1}why didn't you do it right away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:27.30,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,But... it's such a waste to conceal those breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.81,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.18,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,T-That itches...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.49,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,That itches, it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:44.90,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You just can't bring yourself\Nto say that you're hurt or that it's cold, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.11,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,It's because I'm a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.99,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,There they are!  Hey guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.25,Main,They,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heeeey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.56,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Heeey!  Heeey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:14.35,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What are they doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.94,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Everyone, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.56,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Oh, it's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.95,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's Luffy's group!  Zoro!  Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:27.11,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Robin!  Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.44,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:32.07,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Why is that idiot cook so enthusiastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.55,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Is he trying to stay warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:40.83,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What's that?  It looks like a bunch of giant kids, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.17,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh?!  Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.43,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!  Cut it out, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.71,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,We're here!  This place will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.15,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,This equipment looks like the stuff in the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:10.97,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,But it's all in pieces.\NMaybe there was some kind of big explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.70,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Well, as long as they shields us from the blizzard,\Nit doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.49,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,So, where do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:20.29,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,That's gonna leave a scar on my fragile body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.54,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'll take care of you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.79,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Wait, Sanji-kun!  What are you doing with my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:29.09,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.80,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,My lower half has returned to me, it has!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:43.61,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Legson... My hind-legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:51.57,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I told you, there's no such creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.70,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,This is quite surreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.99,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,What an odd fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.41,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,The skeleton...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.50,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Is talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.51,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Nami-Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:16.78,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I wonder...\NI dreamed that I was in a river...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:21.35,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I floated down the river,\Nthrough valleys of giant boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.27,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to have dreams like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:31.63,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Hey, do the tank thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:32.99,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Can you shoot another beam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.36,Main,Child,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:38.53,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:42.12,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Who is he on the inside again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.71,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Huh?  Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.61,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You're having a hard time dealing with this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:53.50,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Let's just calm down and talk this over, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.63,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright!  So, who turned into who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:00.44,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,First off, I'm Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:02.81,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Don't come to me if you get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.89,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.85,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,If you get hurt, I'll treat your wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:10.48,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I'm Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.69,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than fire a beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.99,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,And... We...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.70,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\i1}are Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.99,Main,Usopp & Brook,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:26.68,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I think Nami is being too crude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:32.14,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I won't do it again!\NPlease, don't hurt Nami-san any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:34.63,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Nami!  You'll kill yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:39.48,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,If you touch my body,\Nit'll cost you 200 thousand beli!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.06,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Peeping will cost you 100 thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.26,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,How will I survive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:47.06,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna keep laughing?!  Stop acting like this doesn't concern you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.35,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,So, to start at the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:56.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,this is the samurai from the Wano Kingdom\Nthat we've heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:19:01.49,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,The distress call that we received\Nwas meant for the Crocotaur they called Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:04.32,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It came from one of his subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:09.44,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,This is because the samurai\Nwas relentlessly attacking the centaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:16.23,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,However, I was only attempting to find and rescue\Nmy missing son, Momonosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:19.47,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I merely cut down those who stood in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.54,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,And behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:24.13,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,All these children were imprisoned in that facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.31,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Momonosuke must be in there somewhere as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:30.09,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Yeah, we weren't the only children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:33.65,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,We hadn't even learned all of the new kids' names yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:38.82,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,But the question now is,\Nwhat happened after they sent the distress call?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:41.78,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,It was the man from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:46.08,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,They referred to him\Nas one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:49.39,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:53.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Traf... is one of the Seven Warlords now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:57.05,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Indeed.\NHe joined their ranks during the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.47,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I had been cut into three parts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:05.26,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,My head was thrown inside the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.62,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,My torso was simply abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:11.52,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,My legs seem to have been used as monster bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:16.78,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I was running around, relying on my senses,\Nwhen I must have become stuck to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.03,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It was the back of the dragon's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.99,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you were talking about that "Damn Warlord" earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:28.89,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What?  It was just a pair of legs, right?  How could he have talked?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:31.18,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,That's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:33.79,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Ah, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.21,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,was my farts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:39.92,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,It is a talent I have possessed for a long time, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.97,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You were {\i1}farting?{\i0}  That's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.30,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Indeed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.35,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Ah!  The place is starting to stink!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.60,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,In any case, it is quite comical\Nhow you're just legs and a head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:56.61,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I, on the other hand,\Nencountered someone who was just a torso!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.48,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,That obviously must be this guy's torso!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:01.32,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.02,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Did you see it?!  Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:06.66,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Where did you encounter my torso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.29,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:22.09,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Tashigi... chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:27.19,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:30.31,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whaat?!  Are you really Tashigi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:32.12,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Did your minds get swapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:34.31,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,What's going on?  How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:38.98,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Ummm, are you alright...\Nwithout a heart... Tashigi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:40.69,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Yes, strangely enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:43.22,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,She's acting really shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.40,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:51.49,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,T-This is just terrifying!\NTashigi-chan and Smokey are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:54.57,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,The ships that were hidden near the laboratory...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:57.12,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,had "CC" written on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:22:00.96,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Huh?  Really, Vice-Admiral Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:04.99,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Yeah.  Had they been the same ships that were used here in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:08.80,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,they should have said "PH" for Punk Hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:17.29,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,If we assume that someone above Law\Nis pulling his strings, and that "CC" is their initials...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:20.36,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,then I have a hunch who it might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:26.37,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,If {\i1}he{\i0} is on this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:31.16,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,then it would explain quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.64,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Doctor Vegapunk's former associate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:45.72,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,the scientist...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:47.72,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Caesar Clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:54.06,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,What do you think you were doing, Law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:23:01.77,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I should be the one who is complaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:03.65,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:11.70,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The ruler of Punk Hazard,\Nlocated in the tempestuous New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:15.45,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,surprisingly turns out to be\Nsomeone who has people's respect and admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:19.23,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,As the Straw Hats are shocked by this revelation,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:24.59,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Smoker is about to uncover the identity of Master, who has been pulling strings from the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:25.80,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:26.88,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The World's Worst
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:29.23,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The Terrifying Scientist, Caesar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:31.41,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
